		<main id="main" class="site-main col-sm-12 col-md-8" role="main"><article id="post-11" class="post-11 page type-page status-publish hentry"><header class="entry-header"><h1 class="entry-title">Welcome to Options Schools!</h1>	</header><!-- .entry-header --><div class="entry-content">
		<h2></h2>
<h2 style="text-align: center;"></h2>
<div class="text-justify">
<p class="western" style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://optionsschools.org/covid19"><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><em><strong><span style="color: #000000; text-decoration: underline;">Browse COVID-19 Resources that include a school schedule, food assistance, brain breaks &amp; more!</span></strong></em></span></a></p>
<p class="western"><span style="color: #000000;">Options Schools provide small, personalized learning communities for grade 6-12 students within Hamilton County (in the northern suburbs of Indianapolis) and across the state of Indiana. </span></p>
<p class="western"><span style="color: #000000;">As free, public charter schools, Options supports the academic and social needs of students that haven’t found success in the traditional school environment. At Options, students are encouraged to explore and embrace their individuality in a caring, supportive, and inclusive environment.</span></p>
<p class="western"><span style="color: #000000;">Options-Carmel was one of the first five charter schools in Indiana (opened in 2002), and due to the high demand for our individualized approach to students, Options opened its second campus, Options-Noblesville, in 2006. A fully online Distance Education program is also available to students throughout Indiana.</span></p>
<p><!--


<div class="pull-right picturepadding">


<h3 class="text-center">Click here to watch our video</h3>


<iframe src="https://drive.google.com/file/d/0B0SzjxQ8RGGfNFFKYWp5MFYwUms/preview" width="400" height="230"></iframe></div>


--></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000;">Through small class sizes (15:1 student-to-teacher ratio) and an individualized academic approach, the outstanding and highly-qualified instructors and staff of Options propel students to achieve success both in the classroom and in their future endeavors.</span></p>
</div>
<div class="text-justify">
<p class="western" style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="color: #000000;">BELONG. BELIEVE. ACHIEVE.</span></strong></p>
</div>
