<h2>OUR CAMPUSES</h2>			<div class="textwidget">
<p>Free, public charter schools, Options has two campuses (<a href="/carmel">Carmel</a> and <a href="/noblesville">Noblesville)</a>, in addition to a Distance Education program. Options is devoted to providing an inclusive environment with a student-to-teacher ratio of 15-to-1 and a high-quality, individualized approach. Options also offers dual credit enrollment through Ivy Tech and semester-long field experiences outside the classroom. Start your journey towards graduation by <a href="/enrollment">applying</a> today.</p>
